					"text" : "Shoebox room simulation for a mono source: image-source early reflections + FDN late reverb on a multichannel HOA bus ((order+1)^2 channels, AmbiX ACN/SN3D). Geometry and RT60 changes rebuild on a worker thread and crossfade in click-free. Note: every path (direct sound included) carries a fixed ~53 ms latency at 48 kHz (the FDN injection alignment); compensate when mixing with undelayed signals."
				}

